headline: Why I Just Bought These 3 Ultra-High-Yield Dividend Stocks
summary: Instead of staying on the sidelines, I like to put my money to work when the stock market is bumpy.  Here's why I recently bought these three ultra-high-yield dividend stocks amid the current choppiness.  The reality is that even if Ares Capital's share price goes nowhere, I'll still enjoy a pretty good return thanks to the dividend alone.
